name: Dione Attack Pt. 1
description: You've been sent on a mission of one of Saturn's moons: Dione. Once you arrived there, you can already smell the stench of hell pouring out of the base. It's up to you to restore balance on Dione. EDIT: I fixed some bugs and changed some stuff in this wad update. EDIT2: All bugs found and fixed, thanks to Rob for finding them!
